headline: The Trade Desk stock falls after Amazon offers free DSP testing
summary: Investing.com -- The Trade Desk Inc. (NASDAQ: TTD) stock fell 3% Friday afternoon following an Adweek report that Amazon is offering agencies free head-to-head testing of its demand-side platform (DSP) against competitors.
